<html>
  <body>
    <p>Hi  <%= @booking.name %>,</p>
    
    <p>This email confirms your reservation at <b>Hang Fire Southern Kitchen</b>, Barry for 
    <%= @booking.number_of_diners %> people, at  <%= @booking.booking_date_time.strftime('%H:%M') %>
      on <%= @booking.booking_date_time.strftime('%A, %d %B %Y') %>.
    
    <p>Use this link to view or cancel your booking: 
     <%= link_to "view or cancel your booking", booking_url(@booking) %>.</p>
    
     <p>At busy times your table will need to be vacated after you have finished your meal, but we will always try to accommodate special requests. </p>
     <p>Please try to arrive promptly, if you are more than 15 minute late at busy times, we may need to release your table.<p>
     <p>See you soon and thanks for booking online.</p>
  </body>
</html>